03:28.924 --> 03:30.290
Uh, we need to figure out
the schedule.

03:30.358 --> 03:32.026
Figure out which horses
you wanna take on;

03:32.094 --> 03:33.193
Which you don't.

03:33.261 --> 03:34.729
Get your priorities
straight.

03:34.796 --> 03:36.163
Okay.

03:36.231 --> 03:38.499
Right now, my priority is
the end of School Formal.

03:38.566 --> 03:39.966
Oh!

03:40.034 --> 03:41.534
Yeah. I haven't had a whole lot
of time to shop for a dress.

03:41.602 --> 03:42.535
So, can I look
through your closet?

03:42.603 --> 03:43.970
Yes!

03:44.038 --> 03:46.039
Are you uh,
taking Ty?

03:46.107 --> 03:48.307
Yes!

03:48.375 --> 03:49.442
Yeah, I'm actually
really excited.

03:51.311 --> 03:52.612
Hey.

03:52.680 --> 03:54.313
Hey!
Uh, where were you?

03:54.381 --> 03:55.948
I was looking
for you earlier.

03:56.016 --> 03:57.716
I was just in town
to get some stuff.

03:57.784 --> 03:59.952
Some stuff in town?
Did you get a suit?

04:00.020 --> 04:01.353
A suit?

04:01.420 --> 04:02.855
For the dance.

04:02.922 --> 04:05.323
Oh! No, but I mean, I got
loads of time to do that, so.

04:05.391 --> 04:06.424
You only have a week.

04:06.492 --> 04:07.726
It's this Saturday?

04:07.794 --> 04:09.094
Yeah.

04:09.162 --> 04:10.395
Oh, I thought
it was next Saturday.

04:10.463 --> 04:13.264
Um... okay,
yeah, I'll do it.

04:15.000 --> 04:16.067
"Where were you?

04:16.135 --> 04:18.036
Did you get a suit?
Where've you been?"

04:18.103 --> 04:20.370
Now who's the control freak?

04:20.438 --> 04:22.040
Jesus!

04:22.107 --> 04:23.808
Aw jeez.

04:23.876 --> 04:25.576
Probably the water pump,

04:25.644 --> 04:27.111
Or the... thermostat

04:27.179 --> 04:28.712
<i>or somethin'.</i>

04:30.214 --> 04:31.581
All right.

04:31.649 --> 04:33.616
I'll call my mechanic.

04:35.887 --> 04:37.387
No signal.

04:37.454 --> 04:38.689
Oh! And look at the time!

04:39.991 --> 04:42.392
We're gonna miss the ceremony!

04:42.459 --> 04:45.294
I swear this truck knew!

04:45.361 --> 04:46.428
Knew what?

04:46.496 --> 04:47.863
Knew you didn't wanna go
to this wedding,

04:47.931 --> 04:49.498
so it just up and died!

04:50.066 --> 04:53.102
So now my truck's
capable of ESP?

04:53.170 --> 04:55.037
Oh, so you're saying you
didn't wanna go to the wedding!

04:55.105 --> 04:55.871
Not even denying it!

04:55.939 --> 04:58.340
That's not what I said!

05:02.444 --> 05:04.045
Oh. Oh!

05:04.146 --> 05:05.213
Oh, no...

05:05.280 --> 05:06.881
Oh, no!!

05:06.949 --> 05:08.116
Oh, Jack!

05:08.918 --> 05:16.757
♪

05:16.758 --> 05:24.331
♪

05:24.398 --> 05:26.834
♪ And at the break of day ♪

05:26.901 --> 05:29.302
♪ you sank into your dream, ♪

05:31.772 --> 05:32.671
♪ you dreamer ♪

05:32.740 --> 05:35.708
♪ oh, oh, oh... ♪

05:35.776 --> 05:38.111
♪ You dreamer, ♪

05:40.114 --> 05:42.148
♪ you dreamer. ♪

05:43.148 --> 05:48.148
<font color="#FF8C00">Sync & corrections by Alice</font>
